data.description: Newly Remodeled Beauty in Stockton! This stunning 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home at 1020 W Poplar Street offers both style and convenience in a prime location just steps away from Yosemite Shopping Center and Victory Park. Completely renovated, it boasts new granite countertops, kitchen cabinets, windows, roof, and flooring, among many other upgrades. The updated electrical system ensures modern functionality. With a spacious layout, laminate flooring, and ceiling fans throughout, you'll stay cool during hot Stockton summers. The detached garage presents the possibility of an ADU for rental income or a guest house. The kitchen shines with full backsplash, two-tone cabinets, a wine refrigerator, pull-out spice rack, and stainless steel appliances, including a farmhouse sink. With 1,435 square feet of living space, don't miss this opportunity to call this beautifully remodeled property home!
